UINT16_MAX
===
> Maximum unsigned 16-bit integer.

<!-- <usage> -->
## Usage

``` javascript
var UINT16_MAX = require( '@stdlib/math/constants/uint16-max' );
```

#### UINT16_MAX

Maximum unsigned 16-bit integer.

``` javascript
UINT16_MAX === Math.pow( 2, 16 ) - 1;
```
<!-- </usage> -->

<!-- <examples> -->
## Examples

``` javascript
var UINT16_MAX = require( '@stdlib/math/constants/uint16-max' );

console.log( UINT16_MAX );
// returns 65535
```
<!-- </examples> -->
